


Step 1 --> index.js me jake App component ko React.StrictMode aur BrowserRouter ke andar wrap karo aur BrowserRouter ko index.js me 
           import bhi karo (BrowserRouter ko install bhi karna hai BrowserRouter me wrap karne se pehle)


Step 2 ---> fir App.js me jake Routes import karo aur Home ke liye ek route banao with path = "/"


Step 3 ---> fir 'components' folder create karo usme 'core' folder create karo fir 'core' folder me 'HomePage' file create karo


Step 4 ---> 'pages' naam ka ek folder create karo jisme 'Home.jsx' naam ka file create karo aur 'Home.jsx' file ko App.js me 
             import karo fir Home.jsx me codes likhna start karo (iss Home.jsx mein StudyNotion ke Home Page hai)


Step 5 ---> HomePage pe jo texts highlighted hain una ek component banao HighlightText.jsx naam ka'components/core/HighlightText.jsx'
 
































